#: indices_literature.xhp
msgctxt ""
"indices_literature.xhp\n"
"par_id3155864\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A bibliography is a list of works that you reference in a document."
msgstr "參考文獻目錄是您在文件中所參照著作的清單。"

#: indices_literature.xhp
msgctxt ""
"indices_literature.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153402\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Storing Bibliographic Information"
