msgstr "在「預設」段落樣式中按一下滑鼠右鍵，並選擇<emph>[變更]</emph>。"

#: numbering_lines.xhp
msgctxt ""
"numbering_lines.xhp\n"
"par_id3150222\n"
"help.text"
msgid "All paragraph styles are based on the \"Default\" style."
msgstr "所有的段落樣式都以「預設」樣式為基礎。"

#: numbering_lines.xhp
msgctxt ""
"numbering_lines.xhp\n"
"par_id3150931\n"
